                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 23700/14.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Bryan</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-04-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 12, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Hale instructs Minister Bryan to cooperate with Minister Beaupré at The
                    Hague, from whom he may obtain particulars, to secure permission from Government
                    of Belgium for transit of agent and extradited criminal.</p>
            </div>
